{"tid":1682944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「日常戰線」除咗黃色經濟圈仲可以做多步","createTime":"2019-10-30T11:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T14:05:44.000Z","uid":302066,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7773f74bcb7ddea2e19897e5ebc2df0c1074ad12","tid":1682944,"uid":302066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:08:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係睇黃色YouTuber嗰陣熄Ad Block</span></strong><br />\n相信今時今日絕大多數人都有用Ad block<br />\n係唔使睇廣告嘅同時亦有機會減少黃YouTuber嘅廣告收益<br />\n所以日常睇片嗰陣最好熄咗Ad block先 <br />\n或者用電話食一次廣告再用電腦睇<br />\n希望可以令佢地有多啲收入<br />\n例如希治閣就因為表咗態少咗幾條廣告片(直播時講)<br />\n又或者係之前實測綁手跳海嘅燒車<br />\n大J等都係黃到變金<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">食下廣告去話俾佢地知有一大班手足另類地經濟援助佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果覺得可行 歡迎下面拋多啲黃YouTuber嘅名出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7133f53c562143270b790e7f1cb9ba9c1ea6cc","tid":1682944,"uid":108997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:11:44.000Z","msg":"Alfred Chan<br />\n有碗話碗"},{"pid":"0ee047c29dfd53e917699d7fa94efa5be6ac91eb","tid":1682944,"uid":302066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁就唔推了<br />\n<br />\n成波之路都係黃㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2a5daa3d1b2381171314c424ae1e7afdad7a41","tid":1682944,"uid":108997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:11:57.000Z","msg":"112 維園見"},{"pid":"e6b8b9e2dddbc0590f1a5add9807eed99815e6e6","tid":1682944,"uid":108997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:12:49.000Z","msg":"Cat girl"},{"pid":"82a1b971dd76a535fd0962182dada088d9498c84","tid":1682944,"uid":108997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:12:59.000Z","msg":"Bob叔"},{"pid":"02037fadceda8c58dc3a078d118d45b0587135e2","tid":1682944,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dis